last_episode_to_air.overview: Dr. Roberts' fascination with twin patients nearly ruins the annual celebration of RANDAY.

name: Dream Corp LLC
overview: Helmed by the easily distracted Dr. Roberts, a psychotherapeutic facility treats patients with troubling dreams. Roberts employs a team of incompetent scientists to help analyze and record those thoughts plaguing the doctor's patients.

episodes.name: Episode One
episodes.overview: Patient 88 visits Dream Corp to cure his romantic problems under the supervision of Dr. Roberts and his questionable staff. 88's card gets declined.

episodes.name: The Smoking Nun
episodes.overview: Elderly Patient 54 wants to quit smoking; Patient 88 gets stabbed in the neck.

episodes.name: The Predator
episodes.overview: Patients 86 and 103 confront their biggest fears and relationship phobias with help from The Predator and Randy loses a limb.

episodes.name: Tijuana Zebra
episodes.overview: T.E.R.R.Y. the robot feels outdated when he turns twenty-one, and the staff tries to cure his depression.

episodes.name: You Down with OCD?
episodes.overview: Dr. Roberts works with a patient who suffers from severe OCD; T.E.R.R.Y. and 88 compete for affection.

episodes.name: The Leak
episodes.overview: A leak forces the staff to evacuate during dream maintenance; Joey is left behind in the dream world.

guest_stars.character: Joey in the Center of Her Mind (voice)
guest_stars.name: Liam Neeson

episodes.name: Deep Impact
episodes.overview: Patient 21 is afraid to fall asleep; after a parasomnia episode injures new intern Bea, Dr. Roberts drops in to the patient's dream to guide him through the wake of his fears.

episodes.name: The Bullied
episodes.overview: Patient 37 visits Dream Corp LLC for his debilitating fear of confined spaces. T.E.R.R.Y. discovers the internet.

episodes.name: Accordian Jim
episodes.overview: Patient 13 returns for Dream Therapy. After cancelling her last four appointments, Dr Roberts cautiously agrees to treat her. 88 survives a dog attack.

episodes.name: Amnesia
episodes.overview: Patient 62 catches Amnesia during a routine arachnophobia treatment. Dr Roberts attempts to cure him by hand using fundamentals. Randy gets catfished.

episodes.name: Woomba
episodes.overview: A very pregnant Patient 6 visits Dream Corp LLC desperate to be cured of her strange addiction to eating couch cushions. Randy makes a cyst popping video.

episodes.name: Wild Bill
episodes.overview: Roberts' old roommate, Bill Ruff, pays a visit to Dream Corp LLC under the guise of selling bad office artwork; everyone in the staff is charmed except for 88, who makes it his mission to expose Bill's real intentions.

episodes.name: Guys and Dads
episodes.overview: A dejected Mr. Simzer brings his teenage son to Dream Corp LLC for treatment. The staff realizes his son isn't the only one who needs Dream Therapy. Randy loves Mama's Meat Pops.

episodes.name: 88's Weekly
episodes.overview: 88 goes under to get treatment for his "confidence". Dr Roberts tests a groundbreaking new technology.

episodes.name: Staff Infection
episodes.overview: Patient 30 visits Dream Corp LLC for treatment of a long list of "symptoms." A chemical spill in the Lab puts the facility on lock down. A new side of Ahmed is revealed while 88 is put in grave danger.

episodes.name: Pickle Trip
episodes.overview: 88 eats Ahmed's pickle without knowing that the pickle has been pickled. The journey begins.

episodes.name: Dust Bunnies
episodes.overview: Patient 75 comes to Dream Corp LLC to help clean up his life and regain the respect of his children. T.E.R.R.Y. introduces the staff to his new friend Leonard.

episodes.name: Can't Touch This
episodes.overview: Skin to skin contact feels like fire to Patient 66. With a history of minimal human touch or relationships, Dr Roberts prescribes her a Dream Date.

episodes.name: What Happens in Randy, Stays in Randy
episodes.overview: Dr Roberts wrangles Randy for his biannual session. T.E.R.R.Y. struggles with his conscience.

episodes.name: The Krux
episodes.overview: Patient 101 is wheeled into Dream Corp LLC as part of a court-ordered evaluation. Dr. Roberts struggles to navigate Patient 101's subconscious and calls on the entire staff to help contain their most challenging patient to date.

episodes.name: Comin' In Hot
episodes.overview: Dr. Roberts celebrates his new found wealth too soon. The staff neglects a pyromaniac patient.

episodes.name: Monkey Man
episodes.overview: Patient 84 visits Dream Corp LLC for hiccups and will never be the same again.

episodes.name: Tricky Ricky
episodes.overview: A routine building inspection goes sensationally wrong.

episodes.name: Fear of Heights
episodes.overview: Patient 27 is treated for his crippling fear of heights. T.E.R.R.Y. becomes enlightened.

episodes.name: Virgil Bottoms
episodes.overview: Medical phenomenon, Virgil Bottoms, bullies his way into an appointment at Dream Corp LLC.

episodes.name: Where Are They Now?
episodes.overview: Science Probe Magazine is coming to interview Dr. Roberts for a 'Where Are They Now' feature! T.E.R.R.Y. has a meltdown.

episodes.name: Clone Disposal
episodes.overview: 88 dies, briefly.

episodes.name: Randay
episodes.overview: Dr. Roberts' fascination with twin patients nearly ruins the annual celebration of RANDAY.
